{
  "stem": "16503.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 358.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we went into Italy, Naples.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Naples-- they put us onto a barge, like, under, under the, the hulk or bulk or whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not a sailor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and we-- then from Naples, we sailed into Haifa, and they had to dodge the Arabs or whoever was there to disembark us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They disembark us and shipped us right into, into positions into military camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was sent to-- now you got me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I finished in Ekron, which was a, which was a, a base for, like, aircraft, like, [SIGHS] pilot base.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But before that, I was in a, in a hospital base, and I forget the name now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I really do-- can't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was just a hospital-- huge, huge hospital-- barracks, barracks, barracks, barracks full of people injured and not so injured and so forth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because you see, with the dental course, I had a, a nurse's course, so I really did pretty good considering on the minimum of, of education I had.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I came out with a practical knowledge-- not education, but knowledge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on that, I built as years went on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But when I came to Israel, I could be an-- I became a sergeant in the army right away because I already had that knowledge.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were very, very short of people, of any kind of knowledge at the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this was a great bonus to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a nurse in, in, in this big hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I married my husband in February.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, we landed in Haifa on the 1st of January, 1949, and on the 17th of February '49, we got married already in, in Ekron.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
